.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

City: miami, edinburgh, marseilles, london, hamburg
Food: blueberry, kiwi, zucchini, peas, pineapple
Sport: handball, weightlifting, cycling, basketball, swimming
Flower: miamimaster, poppy, iris, daisy, azalea
Job: scientist, musician, firefighter, mechanic, paramedic
1. Food:blueberry == City:marseilles
2. Food:swedish == Job:firefighter
3. Food:kiwi == Sport:basketball
4. City:edinburgh is on the left of City:london
5. City:edinburgh == Sport:weightlifting
6. Flower:iris == Job:musician
7. City:hamburg == Flower:poppy
8. Sport:cycling is in the middle
9. Food:peas is on the far left
10. Flower:azalea is on the left or right of Job:scientist
11. Job:paramedics is on the left or right of Flower:poppy
12. Flower:miamimaster == Sport:handball
13. Food:zucchini == Flower:daisy
14. Food:peas is on the left or right of City:miami
15. Flower:azalea is on the left or right of Sport:swimming

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| City		|    hamburg	|     miami	|      marseilles	|     edinburgh	|     london	|
| Food	|   peas	|    kiwi	|    blueberry	|    zucchini	|    swedish	|
| Job		|     scientist	|    paramedic	|     musician	|     mechanic	|      firefighter	|
| Sport	|    swimming	|     basketball	|     cycling	|    weightlifting	|      handball	|
| Flower		|   poppy	|    azalea	|  iris	|    daisy	|   miamimaster	|
